II.   to process your requests and transactions;
III.   to improve the Susamp Infotech Services;
IV.   to customize the services and/or products we provide to you;
V.   to assist with our product and service development;
VI.   to perform marketing activities;
VII.   to provide relevant advertising; and
VIII.   For other purposes related to our business.
